data.description: Found in central Springfield, this quaint 2 bedroom, 1 bath home also offers a large kitchen and separate dining room. The front porch adds to its charming character. The large fenced-in yard is perfect for gardening, children, and pets and includes a shed. The home offers additional storage in the concrete basement. This could be another property to add to your rental portfolio or a great, affordable home.
